{{>header}}
<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="img-slideshow" src="./images/slider/img-slide8.jpg" alt="First slide">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block" src="./images/slider/img-slide6.jpg" alt="Second slide">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block" src="./images/slider/img-slide4.jpg" alt="Third slide">
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only"></span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only"></span>
    </a>
</div>


<div class="container-fluid align-items-center mt-3" style="display: block">
        <div class="col-md-12 mt-2 mb-4">
            <h2>Thanh toán với LaPaul</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="icon-panel">
                    <img src="./images/icon/icon-home1.svg" class="mb-3">
                    <h3>An toàn tuyệt đối</h3>
                    <p>Mua sắm thanh toán LaPaul an toàn hơn với tính năng Bảo vệ 24/7 và bảo mật bằng công nghệ cao.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="icon-panel">
                    <img src="./images/icon/icon-home2.svg" class="mb-3">
                    <h3>Không tính phí</h3>
                    <p>Không mất bất kỳ chi phí nào với LaPaul, bạn sẽ chỉ bị tính khi giao dịch hoặc yêu cầu thanh toán.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
